Jorge DA SILVA, Plaintiff-Petitioner,
v.
110-112 FERRY STREET, Defendant,
and
XTRT, LLC and TTG Management Company, Defendants/Third Party Plaintiffs-Respondents,
v.
Portuguese Baking Company, L.P. and Hanover Insurance Group, Third-Party Defendants. C-750 September Term 2017
080715 Supreme Court of New Jersey. March 26, 2018

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-000128-16 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied, with costs.
